window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Shannon West refused to just move on. She wanted revenge. Luckily for her, an unexpected event put her right on the path of the voodoo priestess who could help. </p> <p>She gets a couple of dolls, but they come with a warning: These dolls are <i>alive</i>! Treat them well.... Feed them daily.... And <i>never</i> use on the innocent.... </p> <p>But what happens when you decide to make your own rules? For Shannon, life with her dolls means power and success...but at what cost? See what happens when you donâ€™t heed your warnings.... The doll just might poke you back....</p>"; 
